rows.label: tlk44600184_04_msg0001
rows.name:
You're outlanders, are you?
We're getting more of you these days.
Good call coming to the black market.

rows.label: tlk44600184_04_msg0002
rows.name:
This shop only opens at night, and
sells all sorts of things you won't find
through official shopping channels.

rows.label: tlk44600184_04_msg0003
rows.name:
The quality didn't used to be so good,
but thanks to all the foreign trade, the
selection is actually quite decent now!
